summary: A cosmic villain of immense power traverses time and space, conquering worlds to destroy life in the universe. Meanwhile, heroes...
body:
A cosmic villain of immense power traverses time and space, conquering worlds to destroy life in the universe. Meanwhile, heroes from across the multiverse encounter one another in their efforts to save their worlds and, driven by suspicion and misunderstandings, engage in several intense battles.  After this, however, they settle their differences and recognize the necessity to team up and combine their unique abilities to form a team unlike any other–one that will have a chance of defeating their greatest enemy.  

But despite their best efforts, the villain is victorious and all but several of the heroes are wiped out…forcing the few that remain to join together and attempt to reverse the damage done.

Am I talking about Avengers: Infinity War or Super Smash Bros. Brawl

title: Archaic Kinds Of Fun
body:
What’s the most impossible job you can think of? For Jo Holbrook, The Tank, Killer Extradonaire…it’s being a bodyguard. Leave it to Fury to kick it up a notch. Now she’s playing chauffeur for Tony Stark and trying to figure out where her life went wrong. At least there’s pancakes.

For The Record

November 1, 2014DARCY“Yo, Skye! You in here?!” Darcy called out as she walked into Tony’s lab. She heard music, and she knew Tony wasn’t playing it because he was out on a date with Pepper…

Read more…
